Class CalendarDateTime

java.lang.Object
  org.openntf.domino.impl.CalendarDateTime
All Implemented Interfaces:

Deprecated. 

@Deprecated
public class CalendarDateTime
extends java.lang.Object
implements DateTime, java.lang.Cloneable

This is a class that has no dependency to the lotus.domino API. All calculations are done on calendars. This class is used in at-Formula engine. Warning, this class is not yet completely implemented

Author:
Roland Praml, Foconis AG
